          "slidetitle": "Risks of AI-Driven Profiling",
          "subtitle": "When personalisation crosses privacy boundaries",
          "slidecontent": "• AI can build detailed profiles from loyalty data that reveal sensitive personal habits and circumstances\n• These profiles may expose information members never intended to share\n• Highly targeted offers can feel intrusive or even discriminatory\n• Vulnerable customers (such as those with debt or health issues) face the greatest risk\n• Data misuse can erode trust and trigger regulatory penalties\n• Privacy boundaries are easy to cross without clear governance in place"
