          "slidetitle": "Avoiding Discriminatory Targeting Risks",
          "subtitle": "Protect customers through fair, ethical practices",
          "slidecontent": "• AI can unintentionally reinforce bias when loyalty data reflects historical inequalities in customer behaviour\n• Avoid targeting offers based on protected characteristics such as age, gender, or ethnicity\n• Proxy variables (like postcode or purchase history) can act as indirect stand-ins for protected traits\n• Regularly audit your AI outputs for patterns that disadvantage particular customer groups\n• Fairness matters\n• Document your targeting criteria so decisions can be reviewed and challenged if needed"
