          "slidecontent": "• Always question whether AI-generated profiles reflect real customer intent or just statistical patterns\n• Transparency matters\n• Targeted offers can unintentionally discriminate against protected groups if training data carries historical bias\n• Review AI recommendations before acting on them, not after\n• Customers have the right to know how their data shapes the offers they receive\n• As a next step, audit one existing loyalty segment using the responsible AI checklist from this course"
